		<div class="row" id="409f41c6-af29-458c-b228-b616c93f54db">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/facilities-management-development/sustainability/images/building-grounds-earth-day-2019.jpg" alt="Participants at the Earth Day at Ryerson: 20 Minute Campus Makeover 2019 event."/>




					 
